01:37:15,961 --> 01:37:17,546
Don't be shy, Captain.

1030
01:37:18,046 --> 01:37:19,047
Tell me.

1031
01:37:20,299 --> 01:37:22,050
If I want to have a son,

1032
01:37:23,135 --> 01:37:27,097
