01:58:43,165 --> 01:58:44,958
Oh, isn't that wonderful?

1246
01:58:46,793 --> 01:58:50,839
From the only woman that I've ever
loved and given all that I've conquered.

1247
01:58:50,839 --> 01:58:56,887
